config TM1640
	bool "TM1640 LED Matrix Display Driver"
	default n
	depends on GPIO
	help
	  Enable driver for the Titan Micro Electronics TM1640 LED matrix
	  display controller. Uses bit-banged GPIO for the custom dual-line
	  serial protocol (CLK + DIN). Supports 16 segments × 8 bits with
	  8-level PWM brightness control.
